          </p>
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p076/p076_01.jpg",
              class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-1",
              alt: "Tabella × 10" %>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Ogni cifra diventa 10 volte più grande e "slitta" di un posto verso sinistra.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- × 100 -->
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            2,74 × <strong class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">100</strong> =
